---
title: Text Ticker
description: "Words rotate vertically in a loop using CSS `@keyframes` and `overflow: hidden` — no JavaScript."
slug: text-ticker
cssFile: text-ticker.css
explanation: "The trick is a fixed-height container with `overflow: hidden` that clips to exactly one word's height. Inside, words are stacked vertically in a flex column. The `@keyframes` animation moves the column upward in steps — each keyframe pair holds at a position briefly (the 'pause' between words) before snapping to the next. Adding a duplicate of the first word at the end creates a seamless loop back to the start."
---
{% extends "example.njk" %}
{% block demo %}
<div class="demo-text-ticker">
	<div class="ticker-line">
		<span class="ticker-static">CSS is</span>
		<span class="ticker-slot">
			<div class="ticker-inner">
				<span class="ticker-word">powerful.</span>
				<span class="ticker-word">modern.</span>
				<span class="ticker-word">expressive.</span>
				<span class="ticker-word">fast.</span>
				<span class="ticker-word">powerful.</span>
			</div>
		</span>
	</div>
	<div class="ticker-line">
		<span class="ticker-static">Build</span>
		<span class="ticker-slot">
			<div class="ticker-inner">
				<span class="ticker-word">anything.</span>
				<span class="ticker-word">boldly.</span>
				<span class="ticker-word">natively.</span>
				<span class="ticker-word">beautifully.</span>
				<span class="ticker-word">anything.</span>
			</div>
		</span>
	</div>
</div>
{% endblock %}

{% block html_code %}
{%- highlight "html" %}
<div class="ticker-line">
  <span class="ticker-static">CSS is</span>
  <span class="ticker-slot">
    <div class="ticker-inner">
      <span class="ticker-word">powerful.</span>
      <span class="ticker-word">modern.</span>
      <span class="ticker-word">expressive.</span>
      <span class="ticker-word">fast.</span>
      <!-- duplicate first word for seamless loop -->
      <span class="ticker-word">powerful.</span>
    </div>
  </span>
</div>
{%- endhighlight %}
{% endblock %}

{% block css_code %}
{%- highlight "css" %}
.ticker-slot {
  height: 1.15em;
  overflow: hidden;
}

.ticker-inner {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  animation: ticker-up 4s ease-in-out infinite;
}

.ticker-word {
  height: 1.15em;
}

@keyframes ticker-up {
  0%   { transform: translateY(0); }
  18%  { transform: translateY(0); }
  25%  { transform: translateY(-1.15em); }
  43%  { transform: translateY(-1.15em); }
  50%  { transform: translateY(-2.3em); }
  68%  { transform: translateY(-2.3em); }
  75%  { transform: translateY(-3.45em); }
  93%  { transform: translateY(-3.45em); }
  100% { transform: translateY(-4.6em); }
}
{%- endhighlight %}
{% endblock %}
